===High-tier armour===
The Kodai robes, elder armour, and twisted armours were first proposed in the fourth rewards blog, and was polled in [[Poll:Old School Content Poll 47: Rewards for Raids & Slayer|Old School Content Poll 47: Rewards for Raids & Slayer]], failing the poll by 2.6% of the required votes to pass.

It was repolled in [[Poll:Old School Content Poll 48: Rewards for Raids & Quality of Life|Old School Content Poll 48: Rewards for Raids & Quality of Life]] a month later to emphasise that the set degrades with a 100,000 repair cost for each hour of usage. This failed the poll by 10.2% of the required votes to pass.

In order to assess what changes should be made to the armours to have it pass a poll, a new poll, [[Poll:Old School Raids Armours Survey|Old School Raids Armours Survey]] was made available. After feedback, the final rewards blog proposed adjusted stats, and the final rewards poll, [[Poll:More Raids Rewards|More Raids Rewards]], split each armour set into its own question. All three armour sets failed by around 4%.



